1 TRACT, ACCOUNTING FOR THE EXISTING BURDEN AND THE POTENTIAL HEALTH
2 EFFECTS OF ANY CONTRIBUTION;
3 (VIII) AN EVALUATION OF EXISTING ENVIRONMENTAL AND
4 PUBLIC HEALTH STRESSORS AND INDICATORS BORNE BY THE AT–RISK CENSUS
5 TRACT OR AREAS WITHIN 1.5–MILES OF THE SITE OR FACILITY;
6 (IX) AN EVALUATION OF ANY ENVIRONMENTAL AND PUBLIC
7 HEALTH STRESSORS AND INDICATORS POSED BY THE SITE OR FACILITY; AND
8 (X) IF AN APPLICANT MAINTAINS THAT A PROPOSED ACTIVITY
9 REQUIRING A PERMIT FOR A NEW POLLUTION SOURCE OR A PERMIT THAT ALLOWS
