11 COMPELLING PUBLIC INTEREST IN THE AT–RISK AREA, A DISCUSSION THAT
12 DEMONSTRATES THE PUBLIC INTEREST FOR THE ACTIVITY AND ALTERNATIVES
13 THAT COULD SERVE THE SAME PUBLIC INTEREST.
14 (C) (1) THIS SUBSECTION APPLIES TO AN APPLICATION FOR A COVERED
15 INDIVIDUAL PERMIT FOR A SITE OR FACILITY LOCATED WITHIN AN AT–RISK CENSUS
16 TRACT THAT:
17 (I) IS FOR A NEW POLLUTION SOURCE; OR
18 (II) WILL ALLOW FOR AN INCREASE IN POLLUTION FROM AN
19 EXISTING POLLUTION SOURCE.
